        "html": "<p><em>Oh Valley, your love is a home for the soul's joy</em><br /><em>Whenever I see you my heart grows</em><br /><em>My love for you is obvious and everyone sees</em><br /><em>As tears run down my cheeks</em><br /><em>I come to you in longing full of pains</em><br /><em>My soul returns to me as I approach your grounds</em><br /><em>I walk in your trail in slopes and curves</em><br /><em>My longing to see you never stops</em><br /><em>Being separated from you is a loss</em><br /><em>While I watch the freedom of your birds</em><br /><br />–Seliman Abdel Rahman</p>"
